---
description: Mobile architecture rules
globs:
  - mobile/**
alwaysApply: false
---

Mobile app rules:
- map is the primary interface
- mobile uses Maps SDK only
- Google Places / Matrix / Directions stay on backend
- support walking and driving modes
- vehicle mode is minimal UI and audio-first
- no overloaded controls
- prefer simple state flows and predictable API integration

Mobile owns:
- map rendering
- location tracking
- ping loop
- audio playback
- active POI UI
- minimal story controls